---
title: Speedy Veggie Beany Stew with Easy Rice, Cheese and Soured Cream
description: Looking for a quick and tasty midweek dinner option? Try cooking up our Speedy Veggie Beany Stew in just 20 minutes for a delicious and speedy meal.
